          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-19577 o2iblnd: don't destroy fmr pools under spinlock",
        "message": "LU-19577 o2iblnd: don't destroy fmr pools under spinlock\n\nAvoid use of kiblnd_destroy_fmr_pool_list under spinlock.\nThis destroys FMR/FRMR pools under spinlock which leads\ninto ib_dereg_mr() call which sleeps and causes\n'BUG: scheduling while atomic' when executing rmmod.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=sanity-lnet\nFixes: 44f01c9b7e93 (\"LU-18966 o2iblnd: Missing spin lock in poolset destroy\")\nSigned-off-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I7b8bdd23cb65e629ea6c916704c32d625591e9e7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
